TopicTitle: KSP Keeps Crashing on loading w/OpenGl & Active TextureManagement

Articles.Content: Is there any other way to get around this, i have switched from opengl to DirectX11 and can now play the game but it crashes in the middle of building now.

Three things, first when you post your error.log and your output\_log, please upload it to Mediafire, Dropbox or File2Web and provide us with a link, it is a lot of scrolling to get through, and helps keep the forums clean. Also please list the mods that you are using, it can help us narrow down exactly is causing the problem.

Secondly, which level of ATM are you using? If you haven't done so already, I would suggest that you try the aggressive version in order to reduce RAM usage even more.

Thirdly, if you are already running with aggressive ATM, try removing mods that take up a lot of RAM.

All the best.
I completely forgot about the agressive version of ATM which I will try as I like most mods and I will upload to dropbox from now on. Thanks
